Text: '
Apollo was worshipped throughout the '
Begin Reference: Roman Empire
End Reference: Roman Empire
Text: '. In the traditionally '
Begin Reference: Celtic nations
k: null
Text: 'Celtic'
End Reference: Celtic nations
Text: ' lands he was most often seen as a healing and sun god. He was often equated with '
Begin Reference: List of Celtic gods
k: null
