Text: ' discerned three components in the prehistory of Apollo worship, which he termed "a Dorian-northwest Greek component, a Cretan-Minoan component, and a Syro-Hittite component."'
Paragraph
Text: 'From his eastern-origin Apollo brought the art of inspection from "symbols and '
Begin Reference: omen
