ItalicBold: 2
Text: 'Hymn to Apollo'
ItalicBold: 2
Text: '2.5'
Close Tag: ref
Text: ' that Apollo rode on the back of a swan to the land of the '
Begin Reference: Hyperboreans
End Reference: Hyperboreans
Text: ' during the winter months.'
Paragraph
Text: 'Apollo turned '
Begin Reference: Cephissus (mythology)
k: null
Text: 'Cephissus'
End Reference: Cephissus (mythology)
Text: ' into a '
Begin Reference: sea monster
End Reference: sea monster
Text: '.'
