Section [1] Roman Apollo
Text: '
The Roman worship of Apollo was adopted from the Greeks. As a quintessentially '
Begin Reference: List of Greek mythological figures
k: null
Text: 'Greek god'
End Reference: List of Greek mythological figures
Text: ', Apollo had no direct Roman equivalent, although later Roman poets often referred to him as '
ItalicBold: 3
Text: 'Phoebus'
ItalicBold: 3
Text: '.'
Open Tag: ref attributes: []
