End Reference: Roman Kingdom
Text: ' during the reign of '
Begin Reference: Tarquinius Superbus
End Reference: Tarquinius Superbus
Text: '.'
Open Tag: ref attributes: []
Begin Reference: Livy
End Reference: Livy
Text: ' '
Begin Link: http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/cgi-bin/ptext?lookup=Liv.+1.56
k: null
Text: '1.56'
End Link: http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/cgi-bin/ptext?lookup=Liv.+1.56
Text: '.'
